sources.title: The Demons of the Past Come Back to Kill | The Calling | Full Movie | Thriller Horror
sources.description:
After the death of his father, a man (Brian Chamberlain) is called back home, but quickly re-awakens childhood trauma causing he and his wife (Casey Turner) to quickly depart, but not without being tormented by demons from his past. Based on the 2014 Short Film, this film is for fans of The Shining and the Amityville Horror.

2021. Stars: Anne Bobby | Director: Corey Norman | Writer: Corey Norman
